beer.beer_name: A Hazy Day In Aotearoa - Special Release
beer.beer_description:
Special Release Beer Style: Double Hazy IPA

This hazy IPA is a showcase of the world class ingredients coming from New Zealand. After receiving so much love from our NZ hop and malt providers, we felt we should showcase just how good these growers and producers are at their craft.

A combination of late harvest and special hop blends from Hop Revolution, doubled down with Freestyle Hops SubZero Hop Kief and a dose of Phantasm, delivered on a base of NZ’s finest malts from Gladfield.

This beer is a flavour bomb that’s juicy, dank and action packed. Chur!
beer.beer_style: IPA - Imperial / Double New England / Hazy

You may not be able to see through the haze, but that juicy, hoppy goodness goes down smooth. What started as a trend is here to stay. That's 495 different beers with the style of IPA - New England / Hazy, Pale Ale - New England / Hazy, IPA - Milkshake, or Pale Ale - Milkshake. Try 5 more for Level 100!
